{
  "texts": [
    "Generative deep learning is reshaping drug design.",
    "Chemical language models (CLMs)which generate molecules in the form of molecular stringsbear particular promise for this endeavor.",
    "Here, we introduce a recent deep learning architecture, termed Structured State Space Sequence (S4) model, into de novo drug design.",
    "In addition to its unprecedented performance in various fields, S4 has shown remarkable capabilities to learn the global properties of sequences.",
    "This aspect is intriguing in chemical language modeling, where complex molecular properties like bioactivity can 'emerge' from separated portions in the molecular string."
  ]
}